data.description: This wonderfully maintained home is just a quick drive to town and still on it's own 2-acre private sanctuary. There are 4 bedrooms upstairs, 2 bathrooms and laundry room that has an extra restroom. There's a bonus room that has it's own entry, adjacent to the 2- car garage to use for guests, an office, mancave or whatever your heart desires. There is also a restroom area in the Garage. The deck overlooks the beautiful yard, where you will find a greenhouse, shed and have room to roam. The kitchen, dining and living room are all on the main floor along with a beautiful arctic entry & wood stove to keep the winter nights warm and cozy, as well as offset heating costs. **Closing Cost Credits available with an acceptable offer**
